					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13575073#post-4742029</guid>
				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13575073/scp-5072#post-4742029</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 08 Aug 2020 15:23:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>BANANASUNITED</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6494835</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Great article overall! The dialogue was believable, and for such an upbeat scip, the message was clear and serious. The one thing that could be improved is the progression. I would have liked to see a bit more of the consequences of environmental negligence in the park, whether sprinkled throughout the narrative or having a new chunk added in the middle.</p> <p>Either way, this was a great scip. +1 from me any day.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
